reviewText: I have always liked movies where parents think their child is better than everyone else's child and they go to extremes trying to prove it. Makes me laugh.

based on the true events this movie has the humor , and also life lessons. will keep you on your feet laughing and in shock by the mothers attempt to finish of her daughters rival. The things you do for your child.
The performances are terrific. Hard to believe it was a true story, but it was. One of the few movies I never tire of watching.
